Forward Email Branding Plugin

This plugin overrides the default SnappyMail login page with Forward Email branding, including:
- Custom navigation header with links to Forward Email resources
- Branded hero section with tagline
- Styled login form matching Forward Email design
- Quick access links to Forward Email documentation

The plugin works in conjunction with the ForwardEmail theme which provides the CSS styling for the login page.

Installation:
1. Enable this plugin in the SnappyMail admin panel
2. Set the ForwardEmail theme as the default theme

Version: 1.0.0
License: BUSL-1.1
